subtitleNullable: Commercial aircraft jpg images for classification problems
descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains 6538 .jpg images of large commercial turbofan aircraft for use in image classification (or however you deem fit).
PROS: All images have been cleaned, cropped, duplicates removed, bad quality removed etc.
CONS: Varying sizes.

I have used this dataset with various other ones to train a VGG-16 model in flying object detection and discrimination.
